{"article_id":"CohYzS0GgnX1lWvc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Thousands of pages of interview transcripts with the participants of the June 2016 Trump Tower meeting shed new light on how eager Donald Trump Jr. and senior members of the Trump campaign were to obtain damaging information on Hillary Clinton","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"- and how frustrated and angry they were","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that the material did not come to fruition .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The nearly 2,000 pages of interviews do not appear to contain information","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that would change the course of special counsel Robert Mueller 's investigation into Trump 's team and Russia .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"But the transcripts","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"released by the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"fill in new details","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"about how Trump Jr. , President Donald Trump 's son-in-law Jared Kushner and then-Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort were expecting a bombshell from Russian lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Rob Goldstone , the British music publicist","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"who arranged the Trump Tower meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"told the committee","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"he was anticipating a `` smoking gun '' from Veselnitskaya","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"when he urged Trump Jr. to take the meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"even though he thought","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"it was a `` bad idea","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"and that we should n't do it . ''","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"`` I just sent somebody an email","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"that says","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"I 'm setting up a meeting for someone","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"that is going to bring you damaging information about somebody","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"who was running to become the President of the United States , ''","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"Goldstone said .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"`` I thought","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that was worthy of the words 'smoking gun , ' yes . ''","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee 's release Wednesday of the Trump Tower transcripts and hundreds of pages of exhibits provide the most comprehensive view yet into the circumstances","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"surrounding the controversial meeting and the details of the roughly 20-minute encounter ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"in which Trump 's team was expecting dirt from Veselnitskaya .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"The meeting","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"-- and whether President Trump knew about it --","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"has become a central focus of Mueller 's investigation into Russian meddling in the 2016 election , as well as the congressional Russia investigations .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Trump Jr. has told House investigators","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that he did not communicate with his father about the meeting","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"before it happened .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"The White House has said","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the President weighed in on a misleading statement","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"his son issued","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"after the meeting became publicly known , more than a year later .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Trump Jr.","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"-","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"who had emailed Goldstone ahead of the meeting about the dirt , `` if it 's what you say","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"I love it '' -","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"told congressional investigators","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"he was interested in `` listening to information '' about Clinton in the June Trump Tower meeting .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"`` I had no way","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"of assessing","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"where it came from ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"but I was willing to listen , ''","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Trump Jr. also said","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"he did not inform his father about the meeting ahead of time ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"because he did n't want to bring him `` unsubstantiated '' information .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"The damaging information did n't materialize .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Instead , Veselnitskaya focused on US sanctions on Russia under the Magnitsky Act","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"that the US passed","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"to punish Russian human rights abuses .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"Trump 's team was not pleased ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"according to testimony about the session .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` Jared Kushner ,","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"who is sitting next to me ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"appeared somewhat agitated by this","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"and said ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"' I really have no idea","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"what you 're talking about .","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"Could you please focus a bit more","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"and maybe just start again ? ' ''","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"Goldstone said of Kushner ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"who was not interviewed by the committee .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"`` And I recall","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that she began the presentation exactly where she had begun it last time ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"almost word for word ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"which seemed , by his body language , to infuriate him even more . ''","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"There is also a discrepancy between the meeting participants","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"about how long Kushner was present .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"While Kushner and Trump Jr. have said","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"the now-White House senior adviser left in the middle of the meeting ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"others","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"who were there","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"told the committee","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"they remembered Kushner staying the whole time .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"The transcripts also detail the scramble","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that occurred across the Trump orbit and for those","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"connected to the Trump Tower meeting","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"after it became public roughly a year later .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"The committee on Wednesday released transcripts and hundreds of pages of related material from nine people","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"connected to the meeting .","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"The documents contain a record of closed-door committee interviews with five of the eight meeting attendees ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"including Trump Jr. , Goldstone , Russian-American lobbyist Rinat Akhmetshin , translator Anatoli Samochornov and Ike Kaveladze , a Russian with ties to oligarch Aras Agalarov .","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"The committee 's documents also included responses from Veselnitskaya , as well as a statement from Kushner and a page of notes from Manafort .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"The committee also formally released the transcriptof the transcript of Fusion GPS co-founder Glenn Simpson ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"who was not at the Trump Tower meeting","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"but whose transcript was unilaterally released in January by the committee 's top Democrat , California Sen. Dianne Feinstein .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Senate Judiciary Chairman Chuck Grassley said Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that he decided to release the Trump Tower transcripts","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"because `` the public 's business ought to be public . ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"When asked","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"if he is satisfied","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"that he knows the whole story now ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Grassley did n't answer directly ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"but said :","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"`` I 'm satisfied","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"that we have a lot of collaboration by different people","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"that were there ,","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"and they seem to draw the same conclusions . ''","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"But Democrats ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"who feuded with Grassley for months about issuing subpoenas","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"to force Kushner to testify","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"and Trump Jr. to return for a public hearing ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"argued","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"there are outstanding questions .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"`` We still do not know the full story about the June 9 meeting or , more broadly , the degree","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"to which the campaign cooperated or communicated with Russia , ''","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Feinstein said in a statement .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Sen. Richard Blumenthal , a Connecticut Democrat , said","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Trump Jr. 's testimony was evasive .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"`` I have no confidence","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"that he has told the whole truth , ''","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Blumenthal said .","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"`` My impression","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"from watching Donald Trump , Jr in that meeting","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"is that he evaded","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"and contradicted himself in many of his answers ,","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"and he needs to come back before the committee","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"and testify in person under oath . ''","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"Following the documents ' release ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Trump Jr. said","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"the transcripts show","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"he `` answered every question asked . ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"`` I appreciate the opportunity","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"to have assisted the Judiciary Committee in its inquiry , ''","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Trump Jr. said in a statement ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"`` The public can now see","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"that for over five hours I answered every question asked","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"and was candid and forthright with the Committee .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"I once again thank Chairman Grassley and Ranking Member Feinstein , as well as other members of the Committee and their staff for their courtesy and professionalism . ''","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"The various transcripts paint a fuller picture into how the meeting was arranged and what the participants were expecting","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"going into it .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"Goldstone set up the meeting on behalf of his client Emin Agaralov , a Russian pop star ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"who is the son of Aras Agaralov , a wealthy real estate developer in Moscow .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"Goldstone told the committee","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"he sent the email","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"to set up the meeting","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"to Trump Jr. , rather than the presidential candidate ,","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"because it felt","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"it was the `` lesser of two evils . ''","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"`` I did n't know","depth":16},{"id":147,"text":"whether this should go to ( Trump 's assistant ) Rhona ( Graff )","depth":18},{"id":148,"text":"for Mr. Trump","depth":18},{"id":149,"text":"or it should go to Don Jr.","depth":18},{"id":150,"text":"and let him decide","depth":19},{"id":151,"text":"where it should go , ''","depth":19},{"id":152,"text":"Goldstone said .","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"`` So I went with the latter .","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"I thought","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"it was the lesser of two evils . ''","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"Despite believing","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"there was a `` smoking gun , ''","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"Goldstone said","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"he thought","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"the meeting was ill-advised .","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"`` I believed","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"it was a bad idea","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"and that we should n't do it .","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"And I gave","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"the reason","depth":18},{"id":166,"text":"for that being","depth":18},{"id":167,"text":"that I am a music publicist .","depth":17},{"id":168,"text":"Politics , I knew nothing about , ''","depth":16},{"id":169,"text":"Goldstone said .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"`` And I said ,","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"neither do you","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"and neither does your father . ''","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"Trump Jr. 's response ,","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"according to Goldstone :","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"`` And the answer was simply ,","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"' I 'm only asking you to get a meeting . ' ''","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"Kaveladze told the committee","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"that he `` discussed no dirt with Mr. Agalarov , ''","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"but he said","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"that he did speak with Roman Beniaminov , a friend of Emin Agalarov , about damaging information on Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"`` Roman told me","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"that ,","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"as far as he heard ,","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":"( the ) attorney had some negative information on Hillary Clinton , ''","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"Kaveladze said .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"Akhmetshin described a lunch","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"he attended with Veselnitskaya directly before the controversial sit-down","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"where he says","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"he was first invited to the meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"and where she seemed to crowdsource ideas for what","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"to discuss with Trump , Jr .","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"When he showed up for the lunch meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"Akhmetshin was dressed informally ,","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"`` I was wearing jeans and T-shirt and things ,","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"so I actually was --","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"when she invited me ,","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"I was slightly hesitant , ''","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"`` I said , like ,","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"'You sure ? ' kind of thing .","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"And she looked at Ike ,","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"and he kind of like said","depth":13},{"id":204,"text":"yeah , kind of . ''","depth":13},{"id":205,"text":"The transcripts also show","depth":8},{"id":206,"text":"that all sides knew","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"the meeting went poorly .","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"Trump Jr. testified at the conclusion of the meeting ,","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"Goldstone apologized to him `` for what he believed","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"was wasting our time . ''","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"Akhmetshin testified","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"that Manafort and others were on their phones throughout Veselnitskaya 's presentation .","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"`` Manafort was like on his -","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"I believe","depth":14},{"id":215,"text":"it 's a BlackBerry ,","depth":14},{"id":216,"text":"so he was just sitting in the chair","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"which kind of goes back .","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"He was almost like lying there , like ,","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"you know ,","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"on his phone","depth":14},{"id":221,"text":"and it 's throughout the whole meeting , ''","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"Akhmetshin said .","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"Trump Jr. said","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"he believed there to be a `` pretty substantial delta '' between the meeting","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"described in Goldstone 's initial email","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"and what actually took place ,","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"he imagined","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"there was an element of `` showmanship ''","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"involved in Goldstone 's meeting pitch .","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"Goldstone called Emin Agaralov immediately after the meeting","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"and told him","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"it was `` the most embarrassing thing","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"you 've ever asked me to do .","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"I 've just sat in a meeting about adoption , ''","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"which is an issue","depth":13},{"id":237,"text":"linked to the US Magnitsky Act sanctions on Russia .","depth":13},{"id":238,"text":"Goldstone told lawmakers","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"that Agalarov replied ,","depth":12},{"id":240,"text":"`` Adoption ? ''","depth":12},{"id":241,"text":"which suggests","depth":11},{"id":242,"text":"Agalarov did n't anticipate that to be the topic at the meeting .","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"Kaveladze told lawmakers","depth":11},{"id":244,"text":"he also spoke with Emin Agaralov about two hours after the meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"telling him","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"`` that it was ( a ) complete loss of time","depth":12},{"id":247,"text":"and it was ( a ) useless meeting . ''","depth":12},{"id":248,"text":"`` When we walked out of the meeting room","depth":12},{"id":249,"text":"and went down to the bar ,","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"he called me ,","depth":13},{"id":251,"text":"and Natalia was present there ,","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"and I said ,","depth":14},{"id":253,"text":"'Oh , well , everything is fine ,","depth":15},{"id":254,"text":"we had a great meeting and stuff , '","depth":15},{"id":255,"text":"because I did n't want to upset her , ''","depth":13},{"id":256,"text":"Kaveladze said .","depth":10},{"id":257,"text":"`` But then I believe","depth":11},{"id":258,"text":"two hours later we had another conversation","depth":12},{"id":259,"text":"where I gave details of the meeting ,","depth":12},{"id":260,"text":"and at that conversation I explained","depth":11},{"id":261,"text":"that it was loss of time . '' `","depth":11},{"id":262,"text":"` She was expecting 'something bigger ' from the meeting","depth":11},{"id":263,"text":"only to find herself headed to the Trump Tower Bar","depth":12},{"id":264,"text":"without what she wanted , ''","depth":12},{"id":265,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":266,"text":"This story has been updated","depth":2},{"id":267,"text":"and will continue to update with new developments .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":535,"left":533,"right":534,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":533,"left":0,"right":532,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":532,"left":295,"right":531,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":292,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":270,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":1,"right":269,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":271,"right":290,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":274,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":273,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":272,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":281,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":276,"right":280,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,"left":275,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":13,"right":279,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":14,"right":278,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":15,"right":277,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":277,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":286,"right":287,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":285,"right":23,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":18,"right":284,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":19,"right":283,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":283,"left":20,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":26,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":531,"left":401,"right":530,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":401,"left":297,"right":400,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":296,"right":31,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":400,"left":357,"right":399,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":357,"left":321,"right":356,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":303,"right":320,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":299,"right":302,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":32,"right":298,"relation":"attribution","nuclearit